fielddes: Stock company number, which equals bq_legal_entity_id
Unique ID assigned by BQ to the Organization.
TICKER of the Organization if it is publicly listed.

Link to the Organization's primary website. A company's website is not usually included in the regulatory filings, but BQ uses alternative methods to identify these links, which may result in occasional inaccuracies.
Stock class series that the stock class belongs to
COMMON; PREFERRED; PREFERRED SERIES A; PREFERRED FF; etc.
Date and time data was last received from the State of Delaware for this company
Most recent bq_stock_group_begin_date of the stock class series
Date at which the stock class series was created
Current issued shares of the stock class series; Most recent bq_stock_class_issued_shares; Often null
Current authorized shares of the stock class series; Most recent bq_stock_class_authorized_shares
Current issued shares of the stock class series; Most recent bq_stock_class_issued_shares estimated
Current par value of the stock class series; Most recent bq_stock_class_par_value
Original Issue Price: The price at which shares are sold to investors during an issuance of the stock class series
Certificate of Incorporation: Official date on which a company's COI is filed and accepted by the relevant SoS for the stock class series
